\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33 ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec... 23 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ed5ng h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ee1 tr\u00ean c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 Ronaldo l\u00e0 7%. N\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c, con s\u1ed1 trung b\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea1t kho\u1ea3ng 10 \u0111\u1ebfn 11%. V\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp, Ronaldo s\u1edf h\u1eefu 50%, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n che m\u1edd nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p kh\u00e1c (kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 46%). \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ngo\u00e0i tu\u1ed5i b\u0103m, song th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a CR7 v\u1eabn ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec th\u1eddi trai tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y x\u01b0a, nh\u01b0ng Ronaldo khi c\u1ea7n v\u1eabn t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng pha b\u1ee9t ph\u00e1 kinh ho\u00e0ng. N\u0103m 2017, t\u1edd AS (T\u00e2y Ban Nha) th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea r\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u1ee7a Ronaldo ghi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea1t 33,25 km/gi\u1edd. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u00e0n c\u00e2n v\u1edbi Leroy Sane - \"vua t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9\" \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, th\u00ec con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m ch\u00fat \u00edt (35,48 km/gi\u1edd).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2u xa, \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League 2017/18 g\u1eb7p Juventus v\u1eeba qua, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t sung m\u00e3n, khi nh\u1ea3y cao h\u01a1n 2,38 m\u00e9t tung c\u00fa m\u00f3c b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p khi\u1ebfn Gianluigi Buffon ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00f3 tay. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u1ea5p CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed, \u1edf bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Real, Ronaldo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tung m\u00f3c ghi b\u00e0n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u1ea1 n\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn CR7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn tu\u1ed5i 40.</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"967","checkdouble":"183885"},{"date":"15:07 09/04","title":"Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 Isco","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/30/man-city-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-isco.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;ma