ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Duy M\u1ea1nh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9 v\u00f2ng 3 V-League 2018, trung v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Duy M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 'tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t' c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng \u00e1n c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 8 tr\u1eadn. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, s\u00e1ng 9/4, Ban K\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF \u0111\u00e3 ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o &ldquo;treo gi\u00f2&rdquo; T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn 1 tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, trong th\u1eddi gian ch\u1edd k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Duy M\u1ea1nh, VFF m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1m \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn 1 tr\u1eadn.&nbsp;\u00c1n ph\u1ea1t cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra sau khi c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Duy M\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF - \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ea3i H\u01b0\u1eddng cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;V\u1ec1 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1edd h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 n\u00ean ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u1ea1m x\u1eed \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 1 tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1edd b\u00ean CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i cung c\u1ea5p h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 l\u00e0 Duy M\u1ea1nh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i VFF t\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng 8 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 n\u1ed9p ph\u1ea1t 30 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng sau c\u00fa v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh H\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2017.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"965","checkdouble":"183873"},{"date":"14:37 09/04","title":"HLV SLNA trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u1ea1i AFC Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/hlv-slna-trao-co-hoi-cho-cac-cau-thu-tre-tai-afc-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-