8</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 3-0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111ang xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Man City sau tr\u1eadn thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Man Utd v\u00e0 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edbm \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, c\u00fa s\u1ed1c th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u1ebfu Liverpool kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n b\u00e3o t\u00e1p \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch Etihad.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao The Kop v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o nhau tr\u00e1nh ch\u1ee7 quan v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t g\u00e2y n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Virgil Van Dijk tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 quan nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ea7u to\u00e0n th\u00e1i qu\u00e1. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 3-0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u00e0 c\u1ee9 cho l\u00e0 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 h\u00f2a 0-0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. N\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau g\u00ec Man City c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gia Khoa \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h<o:p></o:p></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"960","checkdouble":"183899"},{"date":"01:36 10/04","title":"Sao Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y v\u1ec1 Etihad","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/9/sao-liverpool-khong-cam-xuc-truoc-ngay-ve-etihad.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opac