yle></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Man City vs Liverpool, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fernandinho cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Man Utd.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man City vs Liverpool l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ch\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola khi ph\u1ea3i l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd thua tr\u1eafng 0-3 trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch Anfield.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City vs Liverpool Fernandinho to chien thuat tieu cuc hinh anh\" title=\"Man City vs Liverpool Fernandinho t\u1ed1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/sao-man-city-to-liverpool-su-dung-chien-thuat-tieu-cuc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fernandinho t\u1ed1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u0169ng trong tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Man City c\u0169ng b\u1ecb h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Man Utd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn v\u00e0 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edbm l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. C\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 c\u1ee9 thua ai, c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e2n Etihad l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i cho l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta, t\u1eeb MU hay Wigan \u1edf FA Cup \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 Liverpool, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng l\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Jurgen Klopp s\u1edf h\u1eefu phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft v\u00e0 ph\u00f3ng kho\u00e1ng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ti\u1ebfp l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Danilo n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Man Utd, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fernandinho m\u00f3c m\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Man City vs Liverpool: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n l\u1ec5 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi hai th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 nu\u1ed1t tr\u00f4i nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u1ea3 r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 \u0111ang ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn h\u01a1i th\u1edf cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00edch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p \u1ee9ng ph\u00f3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Kh\u00f4ng ai ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n t\u1eeb b\u1ecf c\u1ea3, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League n\u00e0y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gia Khoa \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h<o:p></o:p></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"958","checkdouble":"183905"},{"date":"06:36 10/04","title":"Klopp: \u201cMan City \u0111\u00e1ng ra ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng MU \u0111\u1ebfn 6-0\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/klopp-man-city-dang-ra-phai-thang-mu-den-60.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hove