0.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Man City t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League, Liverpool \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tin c\u1ef1c vui. Ng\u00f4i sao Mohamed Salah b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Man xanh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Etihad.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby v\u00f9ng Merseyside v\u1edbi Everton cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQua \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n Salah b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi cho l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Man City t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Etihad. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf ch\u00fat n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah binh phuc chan thuong truoc them dai chien Man City hinh anh\" title=\"Salah b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/salah-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-truoc-them-dai-chien-man-city.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Salah b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Salah t\u1ea1i Liverpool m\u00f9a n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua con s\u1ed1 38 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 41 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a anh. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u1edbi Man City t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League, ch\u00ednh tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ai C\u1eadp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain v\u00e0 Sadio Mane m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi 1 b\u00e0n gi\u00fap Liverpool d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0 sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i.</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng Klopp v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n Salah b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Roma v\u00e0 Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i m\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City hay kh\u00f4ng, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i: <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp khong qua coi trong tran dau Everton vs Liverpool\" title=\"Klopp kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 coi tr\u1ecdng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Everton vs Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/klopp-man-city-dang-ra-phai-thang-mu-den-60.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Klopp ch\u01b0a kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Salah</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc 100%, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng HLV v\u00e0o ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt\u201d, Klopp n\u00f3i trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. \u201c\u0110\u00e3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c hay ch\u01b0a, ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd th\u1eddi gian tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Salah, nh\u1eefng Andrew Robertson v\u00e0 Alberto Moreno b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Everton cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Liverpool ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n Emre Can, Joel Matip v\u00e0 Joe Gomez v\u1eafng