\">Antoine Griezmann \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 trung phong nh\u01b0ng anh lu\u00f4n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuc soc Real Madrid mua Antoine Griezmann voi gia sieu khung hinh anh\" title=\"C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c Real Madrid mua Antoine Griezmann v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/3/Cuc-soc-Real-Madrid-mua-Antoine-Griezmann-voi-gia-sieu-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Griezmann \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1nh cho \u0111\u1ebfn trung phong c\u1eafm. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi 18 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 8 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 27 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf La Liga. N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn anh c\u00f3 25 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 11 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Griezmann gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/griezmann-chi-den-mu-neu-172-177278.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>M.U mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Griezmann</strong></span>, Barca v\u00e0 PSG c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991. H\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Griezmann</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mua Antoine Griezmann, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</strong></span> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1edd Diario Gol kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1ee7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann lai ghi ban truoc Real\" title=\"Griezmann lai ghi ban truoc Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Griezmann-lai-ghi-ban-truoc-Real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid mua Antoine Griezmann \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf La Liga, Griezmann s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real Madrid mua Antoine Griezmann th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Atletico v\u00e0 Real l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a nhau \u1edf La Liga, b\u1edfi v\u1eady HLV Diego Simeone kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Griezmann, h\u1ecd \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 anh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/griezmann-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dam-phan-voi-barca-180-183819.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Griezmann l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</strong></span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href