_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale t\u1ea1i Real Madrid \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB, Jorge Valdano m\u1edbi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p anh ra \u0111i m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bale kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale t\u1ea1i Real Madrid b\u1ecb ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i. Su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 t\u1edbi nay, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Wales ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u00e0 d\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n nh\u1edb v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013, Real \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale cho Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 mang anh v\u1ec1. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 180 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Real v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch 1 La Liga, 1 c\u00fap Nh\u00e0 vua, 3 Champions League c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u1ecf kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huyen thoai Real giup MU dinh muc gia cua Gareth Bale hinh anh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Real gi\u00fap MU \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/22/dong-doi-bat-binh-khi-gareth-bale-du-bi-tai-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Bale t\u1ea1i Real \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5p b\u00eanh. Thay v\u00ec v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo hay Lionel Messi, gi\u1edd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng Marco Asensio hay Lucas Vazquez t\u1ea1i Los Blancos. Trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u quan tr\u1ecdng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Real, anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale l\u00e0 bao nhi\u00eau</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao khi Real Madrid \u1ea5p \u1ee7 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u201cthay m\u00e1u\u201d h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 Jorge Valdano \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Real c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 11 l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 suy gi\u1ea3m m\u1ea1nh: \u201cM\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, n\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Los Blancos n\u00f3i v\u1edbi El Transistor.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u1ee3i \u00fd \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi Gareth Bale. C\u1ea3 4 \u0111\u1ea1i gia Man United, Liverpool, Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-da-tim-duoc-nguoi-thay-the-zidane-180-183802.html\">Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Zidane?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/gareth-bale-roi-real-madrid-ra-yeu-sach-moi-180-183800.html\">Gareth Bale c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid \u0111i\u00eau \u0111\u1ee9ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-barca-khong-mua-verratti-180-183658.html\">Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-modric-se-roi-real-madrid-o-he-2018-180-183636.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Modric s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-hoi-mua-3-ngoi-sao-cua-real-madrid-o-he-2018-172-183634.html\">MU h\u1ecfi mua 3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-va-real-nhan-tin-mung-vu-sao-psg-172-183384.html\">M.U v\u00e0 Real nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 sao PSG</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"953","checkdouble":"183908"},{"date":"06:59 10/04","title":"Fernando Torres ch\u1ed1t xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Atletico Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/10/fernando-torres-chot-xong-tuong-lai-tai-atletico-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight: