a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fernando Torres r\u1eddi Atletico Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y. \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u1eebng danh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi n\u00e0y ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tr\u00ean b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFernando Torres m\u1edbi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Atletico Madrid v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a 2017/18. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Torres l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Atletico</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFernando Torres gia nh\u1eadp Atletico Madrid t\u1eeb khi m\u1edbi l\u00ean 10 tu\u1ed5i. Anh tr\u1ea3i qua 6 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Los Colchoneros tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 v\u00e0 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng. M\u1ed9t chu\u1ed7i nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Atletico l\u00e0 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p \u0111\u01b0a Torres t\u1edbi Liverpool h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2007 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Torres \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n m\u00ecnh l\u00ean t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Con s\u1ed1 81 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 142 tr\u1eadn cho Liverpool c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1984 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. Cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2011, El Nino b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u1ecdn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n chuy\u1ec3n sang Chelsea thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fernando Torres roi Atletico Madrid he 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"Fernando Torres r\u1eddi Atletico Madrid h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/Fernando-Torres-roi-Atletico-Madrid-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Torres khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Atletico</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 suy gi\u1ea3m phong \u0111\u1ed9 khi\u1ebfn Torres l\u1ee5i t\u00e0n \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. Nh\u01b0ng \u00edt ra khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015, tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n n\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V, anh c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay, Torres c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 35 b\u00e0n sau 149 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n (ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn l\u00e0 t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb). V\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Atletico, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau m\u1ebfn v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Torres ch\u1ed1t xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFernando Torres r\u1eddi Atletico Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. \u0110\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2017/18, anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi CLB \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ra m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 gi\u1edd hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac chia tay. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Torres c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi gia nh\u1eadp Atletico, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi 10 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i may m\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra m\u1eaft, thi \u0111\u1ea5u, ghi b\u00e0n\u2026 T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u n\u01a1i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 m\u00e0 th\u00f4i\u201d, Torres n\u00f3i trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o cho LG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fernando Torres tai Atletico\" title=\"Fernando Torres tai Atletico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/Fernando-Torres-tai-Atletico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fernando Torres r\u1eddi Atletico Madrid h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Atletico, lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. N\u00f3 t\u1eebng l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i CLB. \u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y sung s\u1ee9c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Fernando Torres r\u1eddi Atletico Madrid, h\u1eb3n anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh 1 danh hi\u1ec7u. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Europa League v\u00e0 th\u1eafng Sporting Lisbon 2-0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Atletico Madrid tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-atletico-180-183874.html\">Real Madrid chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Atletico</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/atletico-hoa-real-madrid-diego-simeone-gui-loi-de-doa-barca-180-183851.html\">Atletico h\u00f2a Real Madrid, Diego Simeone g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111e d\u1ecda Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ket-qua-real-madrid-vs-atletico-tran-dau-vong-31-la-liga-201718-180-183822.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Real Madrid vs Atletico tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u