annel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u00f9 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, nh\u01b0ng Pogba th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 MU b\u1edfi l\u00fd do n\u00e0y.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0103n m\u1eebng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, Paul Pogba v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Man City ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho \u0111ang l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao. Nh\u01b0ng Pogba th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 MU b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd \u0103n m\u1eebng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba that vong ve MU sau tran derby Manchester hinh anh\" title=\"Pogba th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 MU sau tr\u1eadn derby Manchester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/toa-sang-o-derby-manchester-pogba-van-that-vong-tran-tre.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 MU v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u01b0 trong hi\u1ec7p 2 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n, trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng cho danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1edbi Man City, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t h\u1ecd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong hi\u1ec7p 2. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady trong c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 CLB d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng&rdquo; &ndash; Pogba cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau FA Cup (\u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft). Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2&rdquo; &ndash; Pogba th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 MU nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c. &ldquo;C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u0111a nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi&rdquo; &ndash; bom t\u1ea5n 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265774\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/08/highlight-man-city-vs-man-utd-vong-33-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/nghi-an-sao-mu-co-tinh-khac-nho-vao-logo-cua-man-city-188-183883.html\">Nghi \u00e1n sao MU c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh kh\u1ea1c nh\u1ed5 v\u00e0o logo c\u1ee7a Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-man-city-23-mu-cau-tra-loi-cua-alexis-sanchez-172-183870.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Man City 2-3 MU: C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bi-de-dau-cuoi-co-sao-man-city-khong-phuc-chien-thang-cua-mu-172-183813.html\">B\u1ecb \u0111\u00e8 \u0111\u1ea7u c\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ed5, sao Man City kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-gui-psg-pogba-martial-neymar-172-183797.html\">MU g\u1eedi PSG: Pogba + Martial = Neymar?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-man-city-23-mu-khong-phai-hom-nay-dau-pep-172-183779.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Man City 2-3 MU: Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e2u, Pep!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ruc-sang-tran-derby-pogba-van-bi-nguoi-mu-chi-trich-172-183773.html\">R\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng tr\u1eadn derby, Pogba v\u1eabn b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi MU ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"951","checkdouble":"183889"}]}